@node About Gbank
@section About Gbank

GNU Gbank @*
a @uref{@value{UGUILE}, Guile}@footnote{GNU @uref{@value{UGUILE},
Guile}@*an interpreter and compiler for the @uref{@value{USCHEME},
Scheme} programming language.}  binding for @uref{@value{UGI}, GObject
