@subheading The name

Unimaginatively named after @uref{@value{USBANK}, Sbank},
unimaginatively named after pybank, a Python binding for GObject
Introspection.


@subheading What else

Gbank is entirely written in @uref{@value{UGUILE}, Guile}, no C
code.


